snippet.title: IF YOU LAUGH YOU LOSE CHALLENGE - Cats & Dogs - Who is the funniest to you?
snippet.description:
Well, don't want to start battle now, but anyways; Cats or dogs? Which are funnier, which cuter, more entertaining? Let us know down there. For us, they are all so ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favourite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
